{
  "stem": "3212.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barrack with the Hungarian women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next to our camp, we were in Mannerlager, I-- I think it was, E or D.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next to us was the camp from the Hungarian women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had tried to send to B Lager, to our parents, notes back that we are here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was around the 7th or 8th of July.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, one of the women-- her name was Agnes Ganzfried, from Nyiregyhaza.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why I remember Nyiregyhaza-- it was a town-- before my mother got married, my mother was working in Nyiregyhaza for a rabbi for 16 years.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's the reason that I remember Nyiregyhaza, in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And her name was Agnes Ganffried.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I gave her notes to throw it over to my mother and father, because we wanted them to know where we are.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she saw us children-- it was very seldom to see in Birkenau, in-- in-- in the camp, children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She threw me a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were so hungry, a piece of bread-- it meant so much for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I never will forget her name, and I always-- when I see an Hungarian person, I always ask about her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I never know if my parents-- or Walter sent notes to his parents-- if they received it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We know only that, on 10th or 11th of July, they rounded up B Lager, the SS, with the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Sonderkommando was the-- the kommando that worked for the German in the-- in the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then you had, in the camps, kapos.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The kapos were in the camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Sonderkommando worked actually only in the crematorium, to-- to do the work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were inmates who worked-- the Sonderkommandos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Inmates, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
